<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY VIDEO RENTALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A look at the fast-moving video rentals in four Orange County neighborhoods. 
</P>
<P>
 Video City, 6390 Santa Ana Canyon Road, Anaheim. (714) 637-0551. 
</P>
<P>
 * Schindler's List (MCA/Universal) 
</P>
<P>
 * D2 The Mighty Ducks (Walt Disney Home Video) 
</P>
