 * 
</P>
<P>
 Josh Stallings of Eagle Rock told his 9-year-old son, Jared, that his brother 
had won an award at camp. "What award did he win?" Jared asked. His father said 
it was for "Best Overall Camper." 
</P>
<P>
 "Really?" Jared replied. "I didn't even know he wore overalls."  
</P>
