<DOCID> 079367 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 15, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 10; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
