<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091594-0323 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 079462 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 15, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
South Bay; Part J; Page 7 
