<P>
 Intile Designs Inc.: A Houston tile maker said Wednesday that it has agreed to 
buy tile distributor International Tile & Supply Corp. in Los Angeles and that 
it plans to open as many as 50 new stores next year as part of a major 
expansion push. 
</P>
